tspan.tspan: "In a world where science dared to challenge time itself... one teenager finds himself at the mercy of the unknown."
"After a failed experiment meant to only imagine time travel... actually worked—he was pulled into a strange, unforgiving
timeline. No humans. No help. Only danger."
"Now, everything wants him dead. Every step forward brings him face to face with twisted enemies beyond imagination."
"His only chance? Harvest the parts they guard... piece by piece... to rebuild a teleporter that might return him home."
"But time is no longer his ally... and the future? It's anything but certain."
